# 🏥 Create Medical Record — Implementation Guide (Cubit + Performance)

> **Architecture:** MVVM · **State:** Cubit (flutter_bloc) · **Network:** Dio · **DI:** get_it  
> **Key challenge:** `multipart/form-data` with file uploads + linking two Cubits with zero unnecessary rebuilds.

