## 1. API Reference

| Action | Method | Endpoint | Content-Type | Success Code |
|--------|--------|----------|--------------|:------------:|
| Create Record | `POST` | `medical-records` | `multipart/form-data` | `201` |

### Request Fields (Form-Data)

| Field | Type | Required |
|-------|------|:--------:|
| `profile_id` | `string (uuid)` | ✅ |
| `disease_name` | `string` | ✅ |
| `notes` | `string` | ❌ |
| `record_date` | `string (YYYY-MM-DD)` | ✅ |
| `attachment_types` | `array<string>` | ✅ |
| [files](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/features/medical_records/veiw_model/add_record_step_four_state.dart#26-36) | `array<file>` | ✅ |

### Success Response — `201`

```json
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "data": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "profile_id": "uuid",
    "disease_name": "string",
    "notes": "string",
    "record_date": "2026-03-03",
    "created_at": "2026-03-03T13:09:11.387Z",
    "attachments": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "record_id": "uuid",
        "file_url": "string",
        "attachment_type": "X-ray",
        "file_name": "string"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

