## 2. Extend DioHelper — `postFormData`

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The existing [postData](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/dio_helper.dart#32-39) sends JSON. File uploads require Dio's `FormData`. Add this method inside [DioHelper](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/core/Services/dio_helper.dart#5-64):

```dart
/// Sends POST with multipart/form-data (file uploads).
static Future<Response> postFormData({
  required String url,
  Map<String, dynamic>? query,
  required FormData data,
}) async {
  return dio!.post(url, queryParameters: query, data: data);
}
```

