## 8. UI Integration — Zero Irrelevant Rebuilds

### 8.1 Architecture overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Shared scope (e.g. above the step navigator)"
        ACUBIT["AddRecordStepFourCubit<br/>File picking / deletion"]
        CCUBIT["CreateRecordCubit<br/>API submission"]
    end

    STEP4["Step 4 — Upload Files"]
    STEP5["Step 5 — Review & Submit"]

    STEP4 -->|"reads & mutates"| ACUBIT
    STEP5 -->|"reads files"| ACUBIT
    STEP5 -->|"calls submit()"| CCUBIT
    STEP5 -->|"listens to state"| CCUBIT
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Both cubits must be provided ABOVE the step navigator** (not inside individual step screens) so they survive GoRouter pushes and share state across steps.

### 8.2 Providing both Cubits at the flow root

```dart
// Where the add-record flow starts (router config or parent wrapper)
MultiBlocProvider(
  providers: [
    BlocProvider(create: (_) => AddRecordStepFourCubit()),
    BlocProvider(create: (_) => CreateRecordCubit()),
  ],
  child: const AddRecordFlowNavigator(), // your step host
);
```

> [!WARNING]
> **Remove** the local `BlocProvider(create: (_) => AddRecordStepFourCubit())` that currently exists inside `AddRecordForthStep.build()` (line 91-92 of [add_record_forth_step.dart](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/features/medical_records/veiw/add_record_forth_step.dart)). It must live at the shared scope above.

### 8.3 Step 4 — File Upload Screen (no changes needed)

Step 4 already consumes [AddRecordStepFourCubit](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/features/medical_records/veiw_model/add_record_step_four_cubit.dart#7-75) via `context.read<AddRecordStepFourCubit>()`. After moving the provider up, the `BlocBuilder` inside [add_record_step_four_body.dart](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/features/medical_records/widgets/add_record_step_four_body.dart) continues to work — it only rebuilds when file lists change.

### 8.4 Step 5 — Review & Submit Screen (wired to `CreateRecordCubit`)

Replace the existing [AddRecordStepFifth](file:///d:/Flutter_Projects/Cureta-Frontend/lib/features/medical_records/veiw/add_record_step_fifth.dart#12-127) with this performant, production-ready version:

```dart
import 'package:cureta/core/config/routing/app_routes.dart';
import 'package:cureta/core/error_handling/error_handler.dart';
import 'package:cureta/core/localization/app_localizations.dart';
import 'package:cureta/core/theme/theme_extensions.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/data/models/add_record_uploaded_file.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/veiw_model/add_record_step_four_cubit.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/veiw_model/add_record_step_four_state.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/veiw_model/create_record_cubit.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/veiw_model/create_record_state.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/widgets/add_record_review_documents_tile.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/widgets/add_record_review_item.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/widgets/add_record_screen_header.dart';
import 'package:cureta/features/medical_records/widgets/add_record_step_two_bottom_bar.dart';
import 'package:cureta/shared/widgets/add_record_step_progress.dart';
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:flutter_bloc/flutter_bloc.dart';
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';

class AddRecordStepFifth extends StatelessWidget {
  const AddRecordStepFifth({
    super.key,
    required this.profileId,
    required this.diseaseName,
    required this.recordDate,
    this.notes,
    this.onBack,
  });

  final String profileId;
  final String diseaseName;
  final DateTime recordDate;
  final String? notes;
  final VoidCallback? onBack;

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    final colors = context.colors;
    final spacing = context.spacing;
    final radius = context.radius;
    final typography = context.typography;

    final dateLabel = MaterialLocalizations.of(context)
        .formatMediumDate(recordDate);

    return Scaffold(
      backgroundColor: colors.background,
      body: SafeArea(
        child: Column(
          children: [
            AddRecordScreenHeader(
              title: AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewDetailsTitle,
              onBack: onBack,
            ),
            Expanded(
              child: ListView(
                padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: spacing.lg),
                children: [
                  AddRecordStepProgress(
                    stepLabel: AppLocalizations.addRecordStep5Label,
                    progressLabel: AppLocalizations.addRecordProgress100,
                    progress: 1,
                  ),
                  SizedBox(height: spacing.xxl),
                  Text(
                    AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewQuestion,
                    textAlign: TextAlign.center,
                    style: typography.medicalRecordQuestion
                        .copyWith(color: colors.textPrimary),
                  ),
                  SizedBox(height: spacing.sm),
                  Text(
                    AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewDescription,
                    textAlign: TextAlign.center,
                    style: typography.medicalRecordHelper
                        .copyWith(color: colors.textSecondary),
                  ),
                  SizedBox(height: spacing.xl),

                  // ── Review Card ──
                  Container(
                    padding: EdgeInsets.all(spacing.xl),
                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                      color: colors.surface,
                      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(radius.xxl),
                    ),
                    child: Column(
                      crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
                      children: [
                        AddRecordReviewItem(
                          label: AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewCondition,
                          value: diseaseName,
                        ),
                        SizedBox(height: spacing.md),
                        AddRecordReviewItem(
                          label: AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewStartedOn,
                          value: dateLabel,
                        ),
                        SizedBox(height: spacing.md),
                        Text(
                          AppLocalizations.addRecordReviewDocuments,
                          style: typography.medicalRecordHelper
                              .copyWith(color: colors.textSecondary),
                        ),
                        SizedBox(height: spacing.sm),

                        // ✅ BlocSelector: only rebuilds when total file count changes
                        BlocSelector<AddRecordStepFourCubit,
                            AddRecordStepFourState, int>(
                          selector: (state) =>
                              state.prescriptionFiles.length +
                              state.labTestFiles.length +
                              state.scanFiles.length,
                          builder: (context, totalCount) {
                            return AddRecordReviewDocumentsTile(
                              documentsCount: totalCount,
                            );
                          },
                        ),
                      ],
                    ),
                  ),
                  SizedBox(height: spacing.xl),

                  // ── Submit Button — only rebuilds on submission state ──
                  _SubmitSection(
                    profileId: profileId,
                    diseaseName: diseaseName,
                    recordDate: recordDate,
                    notes: notes,
                  ),
                ],
              ),
            ),
          ],
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//  Private widget: isolated so loading/error never rebuilds
//  the review card above.
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
class _SubmitSection extends StatelessWidget {
  const _SubmitSection({
    required this.profileId,
    required this.diseaseName,
    required this.recordDate,
    this.notes,
  });

  final String profileId;
  final String diseaseName;
  final DateTime recordDate;
  final String? notes;

  void _onSubmit(BuildContext context) {
    final fileState = context.read<AddRecordStepFourCubit>().state;

    context.read<CreateRecordCubit>().submit(
      profileId: profileId,
      diseaseName: diseaseName,
      notes: notes,
      recordDate: recordDate,
      files: {
        AddRecordUploadCategory.prescription: fileState.prescriptionFiles,
        AddRecordUploadCategory.labTest: fileState.labTestFiles,
        AddRecordUploadCategory.scan: fileState.scanFiles,
      },
    );
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return BlocConsumer<CreateRecordCubit, CreateRecordState>(
      // ── listenWhen: fire side-effects only on terminal states ──
      listenWhen: (prev, curr) =>
          curr is CreateRecordSuccess || curr is CreateRecordFailure,
      listener: (context, state) {
        if (state is CreateRecordSuccess) {
          // Navigate to records list (replace stack so "back" doesn't return here)
          GoRouter.of(context).goNamed(AppRoutes.userRecords);
        } else if (state is CreateRecordFailure) {
          ErrorHandler.show(context, state.error);
          context.read<CreateRecordCubit>().reset();
        }
      },

      // ── buildWhen: only rebuild this widget on loading toggle ──
      buildWhen: (prev, curr) =>
          (prev is CreateRecordLoading) != (curr is CreateRecordLoading),
      builder: (context, state) {
        final isLoading = state is CreateRecordLoading;

        return AddRecordStepTwoBottomBar(
          nextLabel: isLoading
              ? '...' // or swap for a small CircularProgressIndicator
              : AppLocalizations.addRecordSaveRecord,
          onNext: isLoading ? null : () => _onSubmit(context),
          onSkip: isLoading ? null : null, // disable cancel while uploading
        );
      },
    );
  }
}
```

### 8.5 Performance guarantees — why there are zero irrelevant rebuilds

| Widget / Area | Technique | What triggers rebuild |
|---|---|---|
| Review card (condition, date) | Plain `StatelessWidget` constructor params | Never (immutable props) |
| Document count | `BlocSelector<..., int>` | Only when `totalCount` actually changes |
| Submit button | `BlocConsumer.buildWhen` | Only when `isLoading` flips |
| Navigation & errors | `BlocConsumer.listenWhen` | Only on `Success` / `Failure` — no rebuild at all |
| Step 4 file lists | Existing `BlocBuilder` inside body widget | Only when that category's file list changes |
| Entire Step 5 Scaffold | `const` + extracted `_SubmitSection` | Never (cubit activity stays inside `_SubmitSection`) |

> [!TIP]
> **Why a separate `_SubmitSection` widget?**
> Because `BlocConsumer` sits inside `_SubmitSection`, its rebuilds are scoped to *just* the bottom bar. The review card, header, and progress indicator above it are never touched — even during loading or error states.

